## Definition of done (sync tasks)

Before marking done, confirm in the summary:

- [ ] All relevant **entry points** updated (table row, industry button, toolbar if applicable)
- [ ] **Both profiles** wired where required
- [ ] **All languages** handled where required
- [ ] Backend accepts `connection_profile_id` + `force_push` on touched endpoints
- [ ] **Committed and pushed** to `origin main`
- [ ] User told to **deploy on VPS** if production is affected
